sub_title: MA in Jewish Studies, passion for ancient history, design and storytelling.
summary:
I work as a project coordinator and a researcher in a foundation that deals with Jewish cultural heritage and education. Thanks to my experience as a data analyst in finance I can develop my skills in a field that is more interesting to me - Digital Humanities.

During my studies I took part in projects combining intercultural and minority education, especially concerning the Jewish culture. I co-organized a culture festival, prepared and conducted workshops and taught Hebrew and History in a primary school.
